parameters:
This isn't an ordinary key, it's sealed with
magic. There might be some kind of mechanism.
This place feels a bit suspicious, doesn't it?

Oh! You have quite the discerning eye to come to
my aid! I was about to be in a very dire
situation!

It seems like we already have some comrades!
Please take care of them!
This is my way of saying thanks!
I'm glad it seems like everyone is safe.

Thank you! You seem quite strong. Alright, since
you've come this far, I'll follow you! Leave the
fighting to me!
I'm saved! Nice to meet you.
That's good. Nice to meet you.
A new loli-mon has joined the party!

Oh, right. If I'm here, I know which way to go in
the Forest of Naughty Confusion at the entrance of
the Village of Lewd Demons.

\C[2]The enemies in the vicinity have become
docile after being able to control this Nest Stone
with magic\C[1]!

Do you want to release the control of the Nest
Stone? If you release it, nearby enemies will
attack.
Released the control of the Nest Stone!

\C[2]I controlled this Nest Stone with magic!
\C[1]The nearby enemies became docile!

The loli character who can use fire skills burned
away the vines!

The loli character who can use fire skills burned
away the vines!

The loli character who can use fire skills burned
away the vines!

If there is someone in the party who can use the
fire skill LV1 and there are vines wrapped around
the treasure chest, they could probably burn them
away.
